Place 1 to 2 cups of shredded coconut onto a small plate. On a separate small, plate pour 2 tbsp. BACARDI(R) Superior Rum. Rim the tops of 4 collins glasses by dipping the rim of each glass in the BACARDI(R) Superior Rum and then in the Shredded Coconut. Set aside. Combine all remaining ingredients (except blueberries) into a pitcher and stir to mix. Fill rimmed collins glasses with ice. Pour cocktail into glasses and garnish with 3 blueberries skewered on a cocktail pick.